S.effect: Hela gains a passive ability that allows her, after she secures the final hit on an enemy, to instantly resurrect one of her brothers if they're dead, or give them bonus health if they're living. Hela gets additional 15% Damage Boost.
Venom grants Spider-Man and Peni Parker an active ability, which allows them to channel a symbiote through them, dealing damage to enemies and pushing them back. Venom gets additional 150 Max Health.
Hulk's presence augments Iron Man's Armor Overdrive and Namor's Monstro turret, making them more powerful. Hulk gets additional 100 max health.
Magik grants an active ability to Black Panther, which allows him to travel backward in time while also giving him bonus health. Magik gets additional 15% damage boost.
Adam Warlock shares his cocoon revival ability with Mantis and Star-Lord, allowing them to revive mid-combat every two minutes. Adam Warlock gets additional 15% healing bonus.
Storm and Human Torch can combine their ultimates together to create a massive, flaming tornado.

A.effect: Rocket Raccoon gains a bonus ability that allows him to place an ammo device on the ground. This device grants The Punisher faster firing weapons and unlimited ammo while he's nearby. Rocket Raccoon gets additional 5% healing boost.

Iron Fist grants Luna Snow a bonus active ability, which causes an ice ring to explode around her when activated. This ring launches enemies up and heals nearby allies. Iron Fist gets additional 15% damage boost.
Spider-Man gives Squirrel Girl a bonus active ability, which allows her to web up enemies via a special web bomb. Spider-Man gets additional 10% damage boost.
Hulk or The Thing can agree to team-up with Wolverine with a button press, allowing either of them to throw Wolverine a great distance.

Invisible Woman grants Mister Fantastic, Human Torch, and The Thing a new ability, which gives them increased damage resistance and continually generating bonus health. Invisible Woman gets additional 15% healing boost.
Doctor Strange replaces Scarlet Witch's Chthonia Burst with Mystic Burst, an attack that allows her to fire a salvo of missiles. Doctor Strange gets additional 150 max health.

Winter Soldier gains the ability to jump to a designated ally and do a slam attack. Captain America and Winter Soldier can agree to collide and create a slowing shockwave that damages nearby enemies. Captain America gets additional 100 Max Health and 5% Damage Boost.
Emma Frost can link with Magneto and Psylock to create duplicates of either or both, confusing enemies. Emma Frost gets additional 100 Max Health.

B.effect: Rocket Raccoon and Jeff the Land Shark can interact with Groot to ride around on his shoulders, granting them bonus damage reduction. Groot gets additional 150 Max Health.
Cloak & Dagger grant Moon Knight a new active ability, which he can use to become temporarily invisible. Cloak & Dagger get additional 15% healing boost.

C.effect: Luna Snow grants an active ability to Jeff the Land Shark. This ability infuses Jeff's attacks with a slowing field. Luna Snow gets additional 15% healing boost.
Hawkeye grants Black Widow a new active ability, which allows her to spot and damage enemy afterimages. Hawkeye gets additional 15% damage boost.
